title: Chuck Missler - The 5 Horsemen of the Apocalypse
description:
In addition to the Four Horsemen of the Apocalypse depicted in Revelation Chapter 6, and their contemporary implications, Chuck Missler also explores some of the prevalent misunderstandings regarding the Ultimate Victor presented in Revelation Chapter 19 and unravels the controversies surrounding the Harpazo (or Rapture) which continues to cause confusion among many believers.
